{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ５","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚很快的就到了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳站得疲倦了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他要回家睡觉了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地的黑幕在慢慢的扯了起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切怕见阳光的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在准备活动起来做好汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时都不肯休息的小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候可象一段呆木头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧抱着小脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹲在屋角里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一个大大的学问家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苦苦的想着大大的大问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比想什么算术式子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要想得更难受。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一点也想不出好办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这比三七等于二十一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更复杂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更复杂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到后来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只急得他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘤嘤嘤的哭起来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“吗哈哈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吗哈哈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里来个小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲在这里哭啼啼的，不要脸？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是你呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么哭？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么叫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是想出去玩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那我可以让你骑一骑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这比骑竹马更有趣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要做一个工作模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要做国家的小主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就不作兴流狗尿！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“马爷爷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不要瞎讲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是你是我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐怕早已急得丢了鞍，脱了缰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是贪玩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不是瞎喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伤心的哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁也不来帮助我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要让我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个小人儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就给老山妖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作菜吃掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作菜吃掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想一想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎能不伤心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！……妈呀！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个老混蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他今晚要来把你吃掉吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要哭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快不要叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有好法子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定帮你的忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快快好好的躲起来呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要你相信我，听我的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果老山妖来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看我一定踢得他象皮球一样滚回家。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“马爷爷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感谢你的好意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一向都听老山妖使唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由他骑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由他坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替他拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"替他驮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么肯来帮助我？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我实在信不过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在信不过。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真是小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太不懂世故！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种整天睡觉的懒虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我帮了他多少年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可越帮越穷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越穷越凶越不中用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为他赚来的钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他都白白的糟塌了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的辛苦都落了空！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种扶不起的懒虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我干吗要帮他一世？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对我又十分客气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我帮助你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有我的道理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有我的道理！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正说着说着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖可已经走上了山坡了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着棍子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手拿着两根骨头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一拐的留心着走上山坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口里还大声的喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这下你可再也逃不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不把你吃掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我永世也睡不好觉。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的声音那么高傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么有自信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但又那么慌张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步又向左面右面望一望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远的，他把骨头抛给了狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小黄狗就不声不响的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢着衔了就走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛下了小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛下了这个患难中的小朋友。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}